                    "text_di4fHC": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Shipping:<\/strong><\/p><p>Orders are delivered within 3-5 working days based on your pin code. Free delivery on orders over ₹799. You’ll receive tracking details via email once your order is shipped.<\/p><p><strong>Returns and Refunds:<\/strong><\/p><p><em>Note:<\/em> Sale items cannot be returned or exchanged.<\/p><p>If you're unsatisfied, contact us within 5 days of delivery at <a>Contact@earthenstory.com<\/a> for a replacement.<\/p>",
